Class Env

  • java.lang.Object
    • wcs.core.ICSProxyJ
      • wcs.java.Env
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Content, Env
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    TestEnv

    public class Env
extends wcs.core.ICSProxyJ
implements Content, Env
    Facade to the Sites services. It is passed as the main argument to element logic.
